"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人唔做去做狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n月入一萬同慘過做狗"},{"pid":"7e3144aa7efd22c7a50834cdd34e7f13f88d7a2b","tid":447614,"uid":152224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有人唔做去做狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n月入一萬慘過做狗</blockquote>"},{"pid":"563a2b6a3d76b751fc026608beb7ff959e44968c","tid":447614,"uid":152224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣你老母做雞養你都好過做黑警啦豬閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n警察都有好人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979dc17d085c8f76ba59cc78fcd921e9221a7e54","tid":447614,"uid":24817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"有無過來師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可以講下PMP實質有咩用？ 對條路作用有幾大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4345a96b01417559a75f3b9b163cd0a56f95b24d","tid":447614,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T14:38:22.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f0cd1173c8a1d8ca3639a9d779ef61b037c4cd7a","tid":447614,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T19:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無過來師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可以講下PMP實質有咩用？ 對條路作用有幾大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有朋友玩過，唔開佢咩u，因為實有人起到佢。<br />\n<br />\nPMP係玩既多，仲會安排intern比你做，我朋友係做organising activity。<br />\n<br />\n其實就幾hea既，入面既人應該打曬招呼，勁優待你地。<br />\n<br />\n同mentor傾計會清楚如果唔好彩要當差條路要點行，同埋同佢熟既話，你一入職都有人照下你打個招呼。同佢唔熟既玩完等於冇玩係多份experience。<br />\n<br />\n玩呢個PMP係用黎砌cv，如果你考紀律部隊或者公務員，佢地會睇你係個pmp既表現。入面既人勁投入，個個入曬戲，我朋友洗濕左個頭焗住頂硬上投入足全程。<br />\n<br />\n聽聞玩得呢個pmp，有超過三成人一畢業就考到pi。有冇加分之用就你自己諗既。本來呢個pmp係for考pi既大學生去玩。<br />\n<br />\n你交完表後，大學會選完人（可能睇你gpa)再比mentor果邊選。我個fd就全部中文in既，但佢話其他人唔係，唔知係味見到佢英文5*問都費時。<br />\n<br />\n佢玩完番黎講左成晚d所謂大學生點刷鞋"},{"pid":"1eba3ee66cd20be12438dc38a6ea626e3262c3af","tid":447614,"uid":26505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:08:08.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打報左"},{"pid":"74711c780867a0d085dcceb3365c3312292c01e9","tid":447614,"uid":22584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"收到email講聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89188e2172a9ffbe483d68cf7cfabd47120be2a","tid":447614,"uid":26505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"[AUS2017]大學生輔警(狗)計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/494044/page/5?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/494044/page/5?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n可以過嚟分享下情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}